{{Frame
|Comments=This is a generic frame that captures all kinds of impediments, whether they are obstacles in one's way, restraints, barriers, etc. This frame is unspecified as to the type of impediment. 

It is also unspecified for type of motion (so not necessarily motion along a path). There was another frame called Difficulties_in_reaching_a_destination which was specified for the type of motion, namely Motion_along_a_path. However this was deleted for now. It can be recreated again in the future if necessary.

It has other special cases, specialized by type of impediment.

Its opposite is Enablement.
|Family=Impediment and enablement frames, Motion impediments frames
